author: izaret
title: Vulk
review:
My very first mixel is vulk.He is very,very cool.Here are the pros and cons.

 

Pros:

1.Uses cool,useful parts.

2.sturdy

3. comes with a nixel.

Cons:

1. really small

Overall Opinion:

An awesome set,and cheap so get it!

author: Boycat
title: Vulk Review
review: Vulk is a very creative and cute mixel. I like how he has sticking out toes on each foot and cat ears, along with the firey fingers, well, I don't really have a way of explaining that well but i think the orange fingers were intended to be lava or fire or something like that.
